        "meta_description": "Ready for excitement, adventure and really wild things? The Folio Society limited edition of Douglas Adams’s The Hitchhiker’s Guide to the Galaxy arrives in a spectacular presentation box with DON’T PANIC written in large, friendly letters on the front. A",
        "meta_lang": "en",
        "meta_favicon": "https://www.foliosociety.com/static/version1721892517/frontend/Gene/framework/en_US/Magento_Enterprise/favicon.ico",
        "meta_site_name": "The Folio Society",
